description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 3:

Biden wants to force you to get vaccinated. Democrats, leftists love to exercise power. Clay explains the origins of his term "coronabros". Biden says "350 million" have been vaccinated. Harris is an extremely unpopular VP. Ashli Babbitt's family files wrongful death lawsuit. Dems exploit suicides of Capitol Hill police officers, try to tie them to January 6th. Buck reads from liberal journalist's account of his first time at a gun range.
